Package: memtools
Title: Tools for debugging memory leaks
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lionel", "Henry", ,"lionel@rstudio.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Provides snapshots of the R heap. These snapshots can be
    compared to detect leaked objects. Graph algorithms like dominance
    and shortest paths are provided to detect the source of the leaks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
